00:18:00.859 --> 00:18:05.859
Uh, well we were, you know, six years old. Twice our size was three feet tall.

00:18:05.859 --> 00:18:09.859
If you need any more ancient history, ask the source. I've got an appointment at the student's door.

00:18:09.859 --> 00:18:11.859
