But you will never see her or talk to her again. You got it?

00:21:06.859 --> 00:21:08.859
Call this guy. He'll take care of your story.

00:21:10.859 --> 00:21:11.859
No emergency rooms.

00:21:11.859 --> 00:21:13.859
This is where I heal my wounds.

00:21:13.859 --> 00:21:14.859
Here, get out of here.

00:21:15.859 --> 00:21:18.859
It's a natural grace of watching young lives change.

00:21:19.859 --> 00:21:22.859
It's in minor keys, solutions and remedies.

00:21:22.859 --> 00:21:26.859
Enemies becoming friends when bitterness ends.

