Why would Luther Corp dump their stuff here?

00:26:29.519 --> 00:26:31.440
Um, I'm gonna go take it from some different angles.

00:26:43.740 --> 00:26:51.960
Mr. and Mrs. Kent,

00:26:52.420 --> 00:26:55.440
I have no idea how this could have happened,

00:26:55.620 --> 00:26:59.079
but I'll do everything in my power to find out.

00:27:01.039 --> 00:27:02.960
