00:27:04.420 --> 00:27:06.960
Well, you think that's how you solve everything, don't you, Lex?

00:27:07.700 --> 00:27:10.120
Just sprinkle a little money on it and hope the problem goes away.

00:27:12.200 --> 00:27:13.720
Well, obviously, some things are a little more difficult

00:27:13.720 --> 00:27:13.740
than others.

00:27:13.740 --> 00:27:14.559
Some things are more difficult than that.

00:27:23.200 --> 00:27:26.160
