00:30:26.880 --> 00:30:27.860
Totally off the record.

00:30:31.040 --> 00:30:33.360
Do you ever wonder about your biological parents?

00:30:35.540 --> 00:30:36.660
Every day of my life.

00:30:43.840 --> 00:30:47.740
Looks like I'm not the only one doing some digging.

00:30:47.980 --> 00:30:48.680
