00:31:56.320 --> 00:31:56.920
How'd you do that?

00:31:57.160 --> 00:31:58.600
I hacked into the DMV database.

00:31:58.820 --> 00:32:00.540
See? Sometimes persistence is a good thing.

00:32:00.660 --> 00:32:02.260
Call Metropolis PD. Have them go to the address.

00:32:02.560 --> 00:32:03.240
What's going on?

00:32:03.760 --> 00:32:05.160
I think Lex is in serious trouble.

00:32:13.380 --> 00:32:15.160
You ready to talk?

00:32:17.820 --> 00:32:20.320
You're finding where you should have been three years ago.

00:32:23.040 --> 00:32:24.280
Exposed in the spotlight?

00:32:25.520 --> 00:32:26.980
What do you want from me?

00:32:28.360 --> 00:32:30.100
The truth about Club Zero.

00:32:30.100 --> 00:32:30.180
Club Zero.

00:32:43.380 --> 00:32:59.840
The case is true.

00:33:00.940 --> 00:33:01.520
Excuse me.

00:33:02.380 --> 00:33:03.660
Did you find anyone else in there?

00:33:08.420 --> 00:33:09.660
Do you know where I can find Club Zero?

00:33:10.420 --> 00:33:11.580
You're six months too late, kid.

00:33:12.140 --> 00:33:12.740
What do you mean?

00:33:12.740 --> 00:33:13.340
What?

00:33:13.380 --> 00:33:13.880
It closed down.

00:33:14.340 --> 00:33:15.860
It was an old warehouse on 78th and Main.

00:33:19.680 --> 00:33:20.120
Liar!

00:33:21.100 --> 00:33:23.880
That's what it said in the papers, but that's not what really happened.

00:33:23.960 --> 00:33:24.660
It's the truth!

00:33:25.100 --> 00:33:26.220
Read your police reports!

00:33:26.440 --> 00:33:28.460
I know you covered it up. I don't know how you did it.

00:33:29.160 --> 00:33:30.040
What you gonna pay?

00:33:30.560 --> 00:33:31.080
Who are you?

00:33:33.100 --> 00:33:33.960
Don't you remember?

00:33:35.080 --> 00:33:38.480
You killed me.

00:33:43.380 --> 00:33:58.020
I told them you allowed me to run.

00:33:58.020 --> 00:33:59.880
Have you ever got that damnzne?

00:34:02.840 --> 00:34:04.540
You?

00:34:06.980 --> 00:34:07.980
Did you hide it from your dad?

00:34:08.160 --> 00:34:09.160
Do you gotta be serious?

00:34:09.700 --> 00:34:11.280
Let's find him.

00:34:11.700 --> 00:34:12.619
We'll bring him back, Tom.

00:34:12.619 --> 00:34:13.079
Okay.

00:34:13.079 --> 00:34:13.360
Lastly...

00:34:13.380 --> 00:34:15.380
This is where I hear you.

00:34:15.380 --> 00:34:17.380
No more games, Lex.

00:34:17.380 --> 00:34:18.380
Or to knock her.

00:34:18.380 --> 00:34:20.380
It's time for the truth.

00:34:20.380 --> 00:34:22.380
God is a danger.

00:34:35.380 --> 00:34:36.380
I know you.

00:34:36.380 --> 00:34:38.380
You're the contractor from the town.

00:34:38.380 --> 00:34:39.380
That's my day job.

00:34:43.380 --> 00:34:45.380
Who are you?

00:34:46.380 --> 00:34:48.380
Amanda never talked about her family.

00:34:49.380 --> 00:34:52.380
She said she had a brother in Central City.

00:34:53.380 --> 00:34:54.380
They said he was in prison.

00:34:54.380 --> 00:34:56.380
She was the only person who kept in touch.

00:34:56.380 --> 00:34:58.380
She was my lifeline when I was inside.

00:34:58.380 --> 00:35:00.380
You see, I never had a rich daddy to keep me out of jail.

00:35:00.380 --> 00:35:02.380
I don't understand. What do you want?

00:35:02.380 --> 00:35:04.380
What do I want? What do I want?

00:35:04.380 --> 00:35:07.380
I want vengeance for my sister.

00:35:10.380 --> 00:35:11.380
What do you mean?

00:35:11.380 --> 00:35:12.380
Where's Amanda?

00:35:12.380 --> 00:35:13.380
She's not here.

00:35:13.380 --> 00:35:15.380
She's dead, Lex.

00:35:15.380 --> 00:35:17.380
She committed suicide a year ago.

00:35:20.380 --> 00:35:21.380
And they're in hell.

00:35:21.380 --> 00:35:23.380
And that's because you cut her out of your life.

00:35:24.380 --> 00:35:26.380
She was never the same after Club Zero.

00:35:26.380 --> 00:35:28.380
Jude's death devastated her.

00:35:28.380 --> 00:35:30.380
It was the love of her life.

00:35:30.380 --> 00:35:32.380
And you took all that away.

00:35:33.380 --> 00:35:35.380
She had nothing to live for.

00:35:38.380 --> 00:35:39.380
Who's that?

00:35:41.380 --> 00:35:42.380
Lucky break.

00:35:43.380 --> 00:35:45.380
A couple weeks after Amanda's funeral,

00:35:45.380 --> 00:35:47.380
I walk into a greasy spoon in Bloodhaven.

00:35:47.380 --> 00:35:48.380
And there he is.

00:35:49.380 --> 00:35:50.380
I couldn't believe it.

00:35:50.380 --> 00:35:51.380
Short order. Cooked flipping burgers.

00:35:51.380 --> 00:35:54.380
You know how they say everyone in life has a double.

00:35:55.380 --> 00:35:56.380
I had to look twice.

00:35:57.380 --> 00:36:01.380
I figure if he can fool me, he can fool you.

00:36:04.380 --> 00:36:05.380
Why'd he do it?

00:36:06.380 --> 00:36:09.380
Tom Perole needed the money, and that's when I got the idea.

00:36:10.380 --> 00:36:12.380
You ruined Mandy's life.

00:36:12.380 --> 00:36:14.380
I'd ruin yours.

00:36:14.380 --> 00:36:17.380
Mandy's finally gonna get the justice she deserves.

00:36:18.380 --> 00:36:19.380
You were right.

00:36:21.380 --> 00:36:22.380
You were right.

00:36:22.380 --> 00:36:26.380
The newspapers, the police reports, what I told Phelan,

00:36:26.380 --> 00:36:27.380
they were all lies.

00:36:27.380 --> 00:36:29.380
You want the truth?

00:36:29.380 --> 00:36:30.380
I'll give it to you.

00:36:42.380 --> 00:36:46.380
If she TP's in it, I'll give you the LI height.

00:36:46.380 --> 00:36:48.380
Right?

00:36:48.380 --> 00:36:51.380
Yes, I'll give it buyout price for you after you kill us.

00:36:51.380 --> 00:36:52.380
Twoال

00:36:52.380 --> 00:36:55.380
Well, I'll give you Jessi the contract.

00:36:55.380 --> 00:36:59.380
My word.

00:37:09.380 --> 00:37:10.380
How is he in there?

00:37:10.380 --> 00:37:12.140
That's what happened. Amanda pulled the trigger.

00:37:12.700 --> 00:37:14.920
She shot Jude. I was just trying to protect her.

00:37:14.960 --> 00:37:16.220
I'm through with you, Lex!

00:37:18.380 --> 00:37:20.160
Killing me won't bring Amanda back.

00:37:20.800 --> 00:37:22.099
None of this can change what happened.

00:37:22.539 --> 00:37:23.380
I don't care.

00:37:24.160 --> 00:37:26.099
After tonight, you'll never hurt anyone else.

00:37:26.559 --> 00:37:28.940
You can't escape your past, Lex.

00:37:40.380 --> 00:37:40.880
Lex!

00:37:49.340 --> 00:37:51.700
Get down! There's a man with a gun up there.

00:37:52.000 --> 00:37:52.240
Wait.

00:37:53.460 --> 00:37:55.180
You mean that guy? What happened?

00:37:56.300 --> 00:37:57.559
I have no idea.

00:37:58.480 --> 00:37:59.579
How'd you find me here?

00:38:01.200 --> 00:38:02.160
With a little help from my friends.

00:38:10.380 --> 00:38:12.380
I'm sorry.

00:38:31.559 --> 00:38:32.160
Hello.

00:38:32.640 --> 00:38:33.480
What do you think?

00:38:33.940 --> 00:38:35.400
I'm definitely surprised.

00:38:36.360 --> 00:38:36.820
Me too.

00:38:38.119 --> 00:38:38.840
Where's Chloe?

00:38:40.380 --> 00:38:42.539
She said she wanted to be fashionably late.

00:38:46.640 --> 00:38:47.780
I got this for you.

00:38:49.320 --> 00:38:51.000
Don't worry. It's not a body part.

00:38:52.800 --> 00:38:54.880
It was in the attic with my grandfather's.

00:38:55.880 --> 00:38:57.579
It was taken just after the town opened.

00:38:58.920 --> 00:39:00.300
I figured you could hang it above the counter.

00:39:00.760 --> 00:39:01.640
Clark, it's amazing.

00:39:01.640 --> 00:39:03.220
Thank you.

00:39:04.460 --> 00:39:05.160
You're welcome.

00:39:07.519 --> 00:39:09.059
I better get back to work.

00:39:10.380 --> 00:39:11.340
How does it feel?

00:39:13.019 --> 00:39:13.500
Terrifying.

00:39:14.280 --> 00:39:15.280
Don't tell anybody.

00:39:15.860 --> 00:39:16.860
Your secret's safe with me.

00:39:28.599 --> 00:39:30.640
I get the feeling you're avoiding me, Clark.

00:39:32.340 --> 00:39:34.240
I just realized there's a lot I don't know about you.

00:39:35.280 --> 00:39:37.519
You think my dark past is going to rub off on you?

00:39:40.380 --> 00:39:42.380
I was trying to protect Amanda.

00:39:43.260 --> 00:39:45.360
My father wouldn't have raised a finger to help her,

00:39:45.380 --> 00:39:47.119
but I knew he'd do anything to save his only son.

00:39:47.920 --> 00:39:49.760
So you took the fall and everything was covered up?

00:39:51.280 --> 00:39:52.500
Is that really what happened?

00:39:53.240 --> 00:39:54.019
Is it the truth?

00:39:56.059 --> 00:39:58.660
The truth is I'd do anything to protect my friends.

00:39:58.660 --> 00:40:05.099
It's the only road of faith.

00:40:05.099 --> 00:40:09.099
It's the only road of faith.

00:40:09.099 --> 00:40:09.360
It's the only road of faith.

00:40:09.360 --> 00:40:09.440
It's the only road of faith.

00:40:09.639 --> 00:40:13.059
On this lonely road of faith.

00:40:13.139 --> 00:40:18.340
But you've come Bye-bye.

00:40:18.340 --> 00:40:22.139
Thanks, Clark!

00:40:22.940 --> 00:40:24.700
But...

00:40:25.700 --> 00:40:29.079
I learned a little when I found you.

00:40:34.700 --> 00:40:37.659
Memories of shaking you down?

00:40:37.659 --> 00:40:38.320
We locked the door

00:40:38.320 --> 00:40:39.360
for years!

